rComments: good teacher, cares about his students

He is a decent prof, although the way he words his questions on tests and online quizzes could definitely use some improvement. The course involves  a lot of memorisation, so you can definitely do well if you put the work into it.

Do yourself a favour and switch immediately if you ever get this guy as a prof, IF he will even be allowed to teach again. He was SO bad that by popular opinion he was fired toward the end of the semester. Unclear, total lack of understanding/knowledge of the subject matter, students knew more than he did, also rude. Absolute worst prof ever.

Avoid this prof at al cost. He doesn't care to give further explanations when people don't understand. And don't bother going to see him for help during his office hours, he is USELESS. He had to call a colleague 4 times for help when some students went to see him.

Terrible prof! He was a replacement professor for the original one who got sick. However, he did NOT know what he was talking about and would often give wrong answers when you ask questions! Unclear and condescending, definitely avoid.
